						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Pillar inside the temple of Saṅgamēśvara in the compound of the Mahākūṭēśvara temple.</hi> </p>						

						<p>A.D. 934.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 856, Jaya, Kārtika śu. 5, Wednesday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 933, October 15, Wednesday, f.d.t. ·03.</hi></p>						

						<p>The inscription records a grant by Mahāsāmanta Bappuvarasa. It is published in <hi rend="italic">Ind. Ant.,</hi> Vol. X, pp. 104 ff.</p>						

						</summary>
