<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samadhigatapañcamahāśabda ma
<lb n="2" break="no"/>hāsāmantaratnāvaḷōkaṁ raṇadhura
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dhavaḷa kaṭakadivākaranujjaḷacandra ma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>yagaḷamallaṁ vīragōpāḷa drōhara sanni
<lb n="5" break="no"/>pāta kiṟiya bhairava pratyanta mārtta
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṇḍa śrīmat bappuvarasarssakanṛpakāḷātīta
<lb n="7" break="no"/>saṁvatsaraśataṁgaḷeṇṭunūṟa Ayivatta
<lb n="8" break="no"/>Āṟaneya jaya saṁvatsarada kārtti
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ka suddha pañcamiyu budhavāradandu ma
<lb n="10" break="no"/>guḍa kāvandu nandikēsaramunelluge
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yuvaṁ koṭṭa sindara magaḷni
<lb n="12" break="no"/>jābbeya maga
</p>

